title: The Great Bongo Heist
description: The boys forget to get Chata a gift for Abuela Day and in a panicked move, they pretend that the bongo drums they borrowed from Xochi are for her. Knowing they have to return the drums, Victor & Valentino pretend to be burglars to steal the bongos back.

title: People Pleaser
description: Blossom neglects her promise to Bubbles when she takes on too many things leaving Buttercup and Bubbles to fend for themselves.

title: Knock It Off
description: When the Professor's college roommate sees his old pal's brilliant creations, he decides to cash in on the popularity of the Powerpuffs.

title: Roundabout Part 1
description: Forever Knight finally assembles his Round Table of young but super-powerful Knights, including— Ben?! With Ben's help, Forever Knight leads his new minions in an all-out attack on a Particle Accelerator - his true intention to transform it into a Time Machine and conquer history!

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: El sistema metrico versus la libertad
description: Robin le enseña a los demás Titanes acerca de las diferencias entre el sistema imperial y el sistema métrico.

title: Let's Do the Time War Again
description: Ben, Skurd and Rook find themselves caught in an endless time loop as enemies from the future converge on Bellwood.

title: Efecto Entrega
description: Unikitty y su banda pidieron una deliciosa comida tailandesa para la cena. Por desgracia, la espera para la entrega se está haciendo demasiado larga y hasta el tiempo parece pasar más lento. En un esfuerzo por conseguir la comida más rápido, la banda utiliza la máquina del tiempo de la Dra. Fox, lo cual causa graves problemas y hiere profundamente los sentimientos del Padre Tiempo.

title: Always Say Never Again
description: Tom and Jerry are hired by a British super spy to help guard the Queen's precious objects while they are on display in the city.

title: License to Drill
description: Mega Man teams up with Bert Wily to take down Drill Man, whose plan to construct hundreds of drill shaped high rises has put Silicon City in both aesthetic and physical danger!

title: Cheerleading
description: Brock drags Master Frown along to join him in following his dream, to become the Flyer on a cheerleading team. They team up with Unikitty & the gang and go head to head against Really Old Edith and her rival cheer team of meanies. But when the gang finds Brock is too heavy to be the Flyer they're forced to try a bunch of ridiculous ways to get him off the ground.

title: Freeze!
description: Axel and his team find themselves in a tough position after Ice Crusher makes it too cold for them to fight back at full speed.

title: Saving Faith
description: Lloyd and his team plot to take control of the Oni Titan. Meanwhile in the First Realm, the Ninja fall into Iron Baron's clutches and an old master returns.

title: The Metric System vs. Freedom
description: Robin teaches the other Titans about the difference between the Imperial System and the Metric System.

title: Princess Buttercup
description: When Buttercup starts spending a lot of time with her new friends, a group of bad-girl skaters called The Derbytantes, it seems the Powerpuff Girls are down to two, which delights Princess Morbucks, who wants to fill the empty slot.

title: Bajo los Reflectores
description: Cuando la reportera Verónica Venegas, madre de Lia, hace un reportaje acerca de Los Fantásticos, Strata El Cazador intenta capturar a Hydorous.

title: El eslabon mas debil
description: Lloyd le paga con la misma moneda a Harumi para quitarle el poder a su padre, y los Ninjas aprenden lo que se necesita para ser un Cazador de Dragones.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Man of the House
description: Clarence's first night home alone spirals out of control, forcing Clarence and his pals to wage war against their own home security measures.

title: Fiesta de Monstruos
description: Enid debe tomar una decisión cuando llegan sus antiguos amigos de la Escuela de monstruos.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Porque tan triste?
description: Steven ha escuchado rumores de un par de Gemas que todavía están destruyendo mundos. Si él no puede detenerlas, tal vez Lapis sí.

title: Burlate con Todas tus Fuerzas
description: Cuando Adorabat empieza a interrumpir agresivamente a todos con su nuevo poder que le da energía, se convierte en una amenaza para el reino entero.

title: El Favorito de la Profesora
description: Los ositos van a la escuela para escapar de sus vidas agitadas.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Creek Cart Racers
description: A high-speed race with a high-stakes prize may be too much for Craig and his friends.

title: Cambiando Objetos
description: Axel y el equipo luchan contra la Princesa SugarSalt por la posesión del martillo de Bearbarian, que le vendió uno de los suyos: iGalileo!

title: Aluxes
description: When Vic finds an ancient relic that summons a gang of mischievous creatures, he uses them to do his bidding, which has disastrous consequences.

title: Mystery Sleepover
description: KO, Enid and Rad attempt to solve a mystery.

title: Caza o Juego
description: Después de recibir un billete superexclusivo para Adrenalandia, Ben deja atrás al abuelo Max y a Gwen para disfrutar de las ventajas de ser el único asistente del parque. Pero pronto se entera de que no está solo.

title: La Explosion de Fuego Colosal
description: Cuando Colosal sale de un extraño estado de creatividad producto de una concentración extrema, es posible que haya hecho algo que podría destruir el Valle Puro Corazón entero.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: From Hedorium to Eternity
description: 11-year-old Ben, Gwen, and friends go on the adventure of a lifetime in their own backyard.

title: Veamos el Show de Boxmore
description: Nuestros héroes descubren que las grabaciones de la cámara de seguridad de Boxmore son la cosa más divertida del mundo.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Maellard's Package
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to wait at Maellard's mansion and get a very important delivery.

title: Out of My Head
description: Axel must help Sarge and Bobbie learn to walk in each other's shoes - literally - after Luka unwittingly switches the toys' heads!

title: Ninja Contra Lava
description: Los ninja se encuentran atrapados en una pirámide y deben escapar de la lava invasora para advertir a la ciudad de NINJAGO de una nueva invasión serpentina.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Forced Kin
description: A terrible, evil menace from outer space descends upon Townville. The girls must fight evil with evil so they seek the advice of Mojo Jojo.

title: Pegatrix
description: Lia no concuerda con las técnicas de Pegatrix, pero durante una intensa batalla, debe aprender a confiar en los conocimientos de su Bakugan.

title: Rise and Shine
description: A glimpse at the wild, secret adventures Clarence undertakes each day before the rest of us, and the sun, get up.

title: Political Power
description: The Gems cause a power outage in Beach City, and Steven helps Mayor Dewey do damage control.

title: Zing Your Heart Out
description: When Adorabat starts to aggressively heckle everyone with her new zing power, she threatens the entire kingdom.

title: Forever Road
description: During a drag race, Ben hopes to stay neck and neck with Vin Ethanol and La Grange as XLR8, but when his watch keeps shorting out, our hero must get creative if he is to keep up with his fast and furious foes!

title: Big Trouble for Tiny Miracle
description: Tiny Miracle allows the gang to take advantage of his generosity at the expense of his own health.

title: El viaje
description: Chloe y los osos hacen un viaje en auto para ver una lluvia de meteoritos. Polar, el único que tiene licencia de conducir, está a cargo del manejo, lo cual se vuelve más difícil de lo que pensaba.

title: Los Porristas
description: Brock convence a Master Frown de acompañarlo para hacer realidad su sueño de convertirse en el volador de un equipo de animadoras. Se asocian con Unikitty y la banda y se enfrentan cara a cara con Edith y el equipo de porristas malvados que tienen como rivales. Pero cuando la banda descubre que Brock es demasiado pesado para ser el volador, se ven obligados a intentar un montón de formas ridículas de levantarlo del suelo.

title: La Parisina
description: Cuando Starfire se obsesiona con una cuchara para servir helado, los demás intentan enseñarle que los objetos inanimados no pueden reemplazar a las personas.

title: Marble Madness
description: Steven and the Gems encounter another droid from space.

title: The Belly of the Beast
description: To repair the Land-Bounty, the ninja must retrieve a critical engine component that has been swallowed by a giant scarab beetle.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Sword Heist
description: When a local sword shop sells an ultra powerful sword to Ratar-O, Lion-O decides he has to steal it before Ratar-O can come pick it up. Unfortunately Lion-O is completely against stealing, but luckily he knows someone who loves to steal, Lion-S!

title: Booby-Traps, and How To Survive Them
description: The ninja team up with a reluctant Clutch Powers to enter a mysterious pyramid where they inadvertently unleash an ancient evil.

title: The Demon
description: Chloe and Ice Bear accidentally lose Chloe's prized hoodie to the ferocious dog next store. They go on a mission to get it back.

title: Ignition Point
description: When Finn and Jake sneak into the Fire Kingdom, they get caught in the middle of a Flame family feud.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: El Vientre del Monstruo
description: Para reparar el Land-Bounty, el ninja debe recuperar un componente crítico del motor que ha sido tragado por un escarabajo gigante.

title: Bananas y Queso
description: Duncan está decidido a evitar que el dúo Banana y Queso se presente en la guardería.

title: Dog Daze/In Focus
description: Dog Daze: Lightning discovers a new Bakugan, Artulean, leading to an unhealthy rivalry with Howlkor./In Focus: While Lia's newswoman mom does an expose on the AO Strata the Hunter tries to capture Hydorous.

title: Last Laugh
description: Ben's fear of clowns emerges at an unfortunate time when our heroes stumble upon a wicked circus with a psychic vampire clown named Zomobozo.

title: Balloon Boys
description: Vic & Val go on a hot air balloon trip with Sal and compete to be his favorite, but things go awry when they try to use the magical Nazca Lines to their advantage.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Duncan Duty
description: When Duncan realizes Chef is getting kids to tattle on him in return for chocolate milk he sees an opportunity.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Punos Fuertes
description: Harto de perder cuando juega a los videojuegos contra su padre, Craig busca entrenarse en el Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Dollar Hunt
description: Clarence hosts a fun "dollar hunt" game to meet new friends. But things go awry when Clarence accidentally buries the money his Mom gave him to buy refreshments for her book club meeting.

title: The Inbetween
description: Apple and Onion get lost beneath their floorboards and must find a way out.

title: King of the Machines
description: Panthro gets insecure when he finds out Barbastella has a history of dating royalty, so he tries to impress her by becoming "King of the Machines" and giving all the appliances in the Cats' Lair artificial intelligence.

title: The Fair
description: The Baby Bears make a deal with a carnival worker to be prizes for a game of ball toss.

title: Escape de Bahia Bebe
description: Cuando, por accidente, Vic y Val se convierten a sí mismos y a Don en bebés, deben escapar de una guardería para poder volver a sus edades normales.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Marvolo the Wizard
description: Pops thinks that he's a wizard trapped in medieval times, and he wants to go back home.

title: The Line
description: The family has waited in line outside the movie theater all night. They are devastated when Larry tells them they won't get into the first screening of the Stellar Odyssey sequel. But, hardcore fans that they are, the Wattersons are determined to be the first to see the movie and so set about battling their way to the front of the queue.

title: All Chalked Up
description: Him tricks Bubbles into bringing her chalk drawings to life, who then proceed to wreak havoc in Townsville.

title: Ball of Fire
description: The hot dog relish that Crooked Eddie brings to the detectives turns out to be an explosive device that Tom and Jerry must now return to the lab before it inadvertently blows up the entire city.

title: Grown Up Stuff
description: Puppycorn doesn't want to grow up. To ease his woes, Unikitty spends the day teaching him all the fun things about being an adult.

title: Onion Trade
description: A boy trade between Steven and Onion escalates to epic proportions.

title: Sad Sax
description: Mordecai wants to get back together with C.J.

title: Spa Day
description: The Bears have a relaxing day at the spa. Grizz tries to get everything the spa has to offer. Panda gets trapped in the steam room with an old man. And Ice Bear plays ping pong.

title: Don't Press Play
description: The Titans must help De La Soul save their music after it is stolen by an alien.

title: The Weakest Link
description: Lloyd turns the tables on Harumi to take his father's power away, and the Ninja learn what it takes to be a Dragon Hunter.

title: Trampas y Como Sobrevivir a Ellas
description: El ninja se une a un clutch Powers renuente para entrar en una misteriosa pirámide donde desatan sin darse cuenta un antiguo mal.

title: Power Up Puff
description: During a fight, both Buttercup and Bubbles are surprised to discover they've leveled up, leaving Blossom to wonder when or if she'll get new powers too.

title: Brain Game
description: Uncle Grandpa calls on Pizza Steve, the self-proclaimed master of video games, to help a kid beat a game.  Only problem: Pizza Steve is terrible at video games.

title: La noche que Ben Tennyson vino al pueblo
description: El equipo Tennyson viaja a Wheeler, "la ciudad minera más animada de la Ruta 66". Pero cuando Ben se pone paranoico con la idea de que el Caballero por Siempre lo esté persiguiendo, debe tratar de convencer a su familia al mismo tiempo que evita que su nuevo enemigo destruya la ciudad.

title: The Fly
description: Apple and Onion must rid their apartment of a fly or face eviction.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Dia de Spa
description: Los Osos se relajan en el spa. Grizz intenta usar todos los servicios del spa. Panda queda atrapado en la sala de vapor con un anciano. Y Polar juega al ping pong.

title: #ConoceAGuepardo
description: Barbara Minerva está super celosa de la "pequeña señorita perfecta" Diana Prince. Pero cuando usa un antiguo artefacto de la colección de su padre para lanzar una maldición contra Diana, la maldición se vuelve en su contra.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Plaza Film Festival
description: When the plaza has its own film festival, KO, Enid and Rad are sure their entry will win!

title: Why So Blue?
description: Steven has heard rumors of a pair of Gems that are still destroying worlds. If he can't stop them, maybe Lapis can.

title: The Scoop
description: The Titans find it odd when Starfire becomes friends with an ice cream scoop.

title: Field Trip
description: A group of teenage superheroes are being shown around the Fortress of Solitude when they inadvertently cause the phantom zone projector to trap Superman and release three Kryptonian criminals.

title: Congelados
description: Axel y su equipo se encuentran en una posición difícil después de que Ice Crusher hace demasiado frío para que puedan defenderse a toda velocidad.

title: Ninja vs. Lava
description: The ninja find themselves trapped in a pyramid and must escape encroaching lava to warn NINJAGO City of a new Serpentine invasion.

title: La feria
description: Los Osos bebés hacen un trato con un empleado del parque de atracciones para convertirse en premios de un juego de lanzamiento de pelota.

title: Prey or Play
description: After receiving a super-exclusive ticket to Adrenaland, Ben leaves behind Grandpa Max and Gwen to enjoy the perks of being the parks only attendant, but when he learns he's not alone, our hero must now contend with the only kid who could afford the price of admission: Billy Billions!

title: Road Trip
description: Chloe and the Bears take a road trip to see a meteor shower. Ice Bear, the only one licensed to drive, is put in charge, which becomes harder than he thought.

title: All Good in the Wood
description: When Suna and Ashley's science project turns into a hungry blob monster, Mega Man must team up with Wood Man to shut down the experiment gone wrong before it devours the city!

title: Helter Shelter/Power Lunch
description: Helter Shelter: Bubbles has a habit of saving helpless animals and the Professor is sick of it. When Bubbles brings a baby whale home, she and her sisters have a whale of a time hiding this new addition./Power Lunch: The Gangreen Gang shoplifts from a mini-mart, shoveling loads of food down their throats as fast as possible. When the girls fire at them with their laser vision, a strange reaction occurs.

title: Winter Creeklympics
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP try their luck at winning Gold in their first ever, Winter Creeklympics!

title: Enredos Perrunos
description: Lightning descubre un nuevo Bakugan, Artulean, y eso desata una fuerte rivalidad entre él y Howlkor.

title: BBRAEBDAY
description: Raven's demon side has the same birthday as Beast Boy, so the Titans go to Azarath to celebrate her Sinister Sixteen.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Ninos vergonzosos
description: Owen teme perder a su mejor amigo Noah que se va a una escuela militar.

title: El Gran Robo de Bongos
description: Los chicos olvidan conseguir un regalo para Chata en el Día de la Abuela y en un movimiento desesperado, le regalan los bongos que pidieron prestados a Xochi. Sabiendo que deben devolver los tambores, Victor y Valentino fingen ser ladrones para robar los instrumentos.

title: Hip hip Hurra
description: Bridgette tiene hipo y está desesperada por librarse de ellos.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Slumber Party
description: Clarence struggles to make a connection at an all-girls slumber party, leaving Sumo and Jeff at odds without Clarence as their "friendship buffer."

title: Little Sword of Horrors
description: Prohyas grows a new Magisword from a tiny seed, but doesn't know that his Carnivorous Plant Magisword is a menace to Lyvsherian society until its too late!

title: Monster Party
description: Enid is faced with a choice when her old friends from Ghoul School show up.

title: Grup Jam
description: Grup invents the "new" sport of basketball, but the stakes are too high for the Warriors to let him play the Galacton team, as the winner shall rule the Kingdom of Rhyboflaven.

title: Claudus
description: Lion-O's dad King Claudus arrives on Third Earth, and turns out to be a big selfish jerk! Now Lion-O has to deal with his dad before he goes to war with the rest of the Thundercats.

title: Teacher's Pet
description: The Baby Bears escape their hectic lives by attending school.

title: Delivery Effect
description: Unikitty and gang have ordered some delicious Thai food for dinner.  Unfortunately the wait for the delivery is proving too much, time itself seems to have slowed down. In an effort to get the food their faster the gang utilizes Dr. Fox's time machine, which causes big problems and really hurts Father Time's feelings.

title: Inglorious Toddlers
description: Owen fears he's about to lose his BFF Noah to a gifted military school.

title: Body Trouble
description: When Uncle Grandpa and Belly Bag have a disagreement, they separate and try to make each other jealous.

title: Painbow
description: When a mysterious rainbow causes everyone to become unnaturally happy, the Powerpuff Girls must find where it ends to save the day and return Townsville to normal.

title: #LaCubetaDeBurritos
description: A Babs le encanta su trabajo en el restaurante de comida rápida "La Cubeta de Burritos" , pero a su jefe, que está harto de que ella siempre llegue tarde y de su enorme dispersión, le encantaría encontrar cualquier excusa para despedirla. Cuando se produce un robo a un banco que está enfrente de su trabajo, Babs no puede decidir si encarnar su papel de superheroína o el de empleada obediente de La Cubeta. Pero ¿será capaz de salvar a todos y conservar su empleo justo a tiempo?
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Bananas & Cheese
description: Duncan is determined to stop the musical duo Bananas & Cheese from coming to the daycare.

title: Monster Buddies
description: Steven accidentally releases a monster from a gem bubble and attempts to tame its wild, violent instincts.

title: Serpientastrofe
description: El ataque de Serpentine en NINJAGO City se ve desde una perspectiva inesperada, completamente al estilo de un noticiero en vivo entregado por Gayle Gossip y su camarógrafo.

title: Frenemies/Strata's Fear
description: Frenemies: Two new Bakugan Brawlers, Shun and Magnus, try out for the AO./Strata's Fear: The AO solve the mystery of a kid's missing Bakugan and meet a Bakugan Hunter named Strata.

title: The News Never Sleeps!
description: Lil' Nelson takes a job as a paperboy, which is more difficult than it sounds in a city overrun by scorching Pyro Vipers and an evil Serpentine sorceress.

title: Birdman
description: When Birdman makes the RV's attic his new home, Uncle Grandpa and the gang must figure out a way to make him leave before they're all driven crazy.

title: Welcome to Creek Street
description: Craig and his friends create their own neighborhood in the snow!

title: Kevin 11
description: After a big argument with Max, Ben rebels by going out on his own in the Big Apple and makes friends with Kevin 11, who has plans for the Omnitrix.

title: Hic Hic Hooray
description: Bridgette gets the hiccups and becomes desperate to get rid of them.

title: The Music Store Thief
description: Apple and Onion have to defend the music store from instrument theft to get a key to the store.

title: Dia de elecciones
description: En un esfuerzo por demostrarle a Master Frown que no es una tirana, Unikitty acuerda celebrar una elección para ver quién será la nueva princesa del Unireino. En una situación sorpresiva, Master Frown toma una ventaja temprana en las encuestas. Unikitty descubre que Frown gana porque está haciendo trampa. ¿Recurrirá Unikitty a sus propios trucos sucios para ganar las elecciones o permanecerá fiel a sí misma y seguirá tratando de ganar gracias a su amabilidad?

title: The Limit
description: The Watterson family faces Mom's wrath in a supermarket.

title: Lecciones para un maestro
description: Cuando el Barón de Hierro obliga a Wu a tomar la Armadura de Dragón, las cosas no salen como se planearon. En Ninjago, hay un límite de lo que Lloyd puede soportar mientras se aferra a la esperanza del regreso de los Ninjas.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: The Lesson
description: Gumball and Darwin get put in detention and quickly find it's more like prison than school. And there's only one thing to do in prison... ESCAPE!

title: El Miedo de Strata
description: Los Fantásticos resuelven la misteriosa desaparición del Bakugan de un niño, y conocen a un cazador de Bakugan llamado Strata.

title: Champions of Breakfast
description: An epic battle between Vambre and her Waffle Magisword and Prohyas' Pancake Magisword escalates to a war that can only end when Grup solicits his Cave Weirdo pals to be peacemakers.

title: The Tome of Morrow
description: Noville's Magisword training with Vambre pays off and the Warriors invite him on a mission to an ancient cave in the Barren Faceland to find the rare and sacred book, the Tome of Morrow.

title: In Your Footsteps
description: A bear befriends Finn and Jake, but what are his true intentions?

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Big Bad Dreams
description: When Namagem starts using his Hypno powers to haunt Aki's dreams, our hero must face his fears in the dreamscape.

title: The Laziest
description: Gumball and Darwin challenge Dad to a "lazy-off."

title: Salchichas y Dulce Golpe
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben superar sus obsesiones por las salchichas y los videojuegos.

title: Poorbucks
description: When Morbucks loses her money, Blossom tries to reform her.

title: Mall-Ra
description: Mumm-Ra builds a mall that's actually a giant labyrinth designed to trap the Thundercats forever. Too bad the Thundercats love the mall so much they could literally spend all eternity there.

title: Lucky Girl
description: Ben battles an evil sorcerer whose power whose emanates from mystic charms, one of which turns Gwen into her own superhero named Lucky Girl.

title: Carretera por Siempre
description: Durante una carrera de aceleración, Ben espera mantenerse al mismo nivel con Vin Etanol y La Grange como XLR8. Pero cuando su reloj hace cortocircuito una y otra vez, nuestro héroe debe ser creativo si quiere seguir el ritmo de sus rápidos y furiosos enemigos.

title: It Was Them
description: Dr. Animo has escaped his Plumber prison, and Ben and Rook must track him down before he turns the world into his personal mutant ant farm! (Introducing Nemetrix alien Slamworm, Galvan Plumbers Blukic and Driba, Arctiguana, new Ben alien Crashhopper.)

title: Acceso Denegado
description: Cuando Axel y el equipo intentan descubrir cuál es el arma secreta de Sarge Charge, son expulsados ​​de la casa por su sistema de seguridad recientemente actualizado y deben abrirse camino antes de que Madcap lo haga.

title: Ninos de Globo
description: Vic y Val salen de viaje en globo aerostático con Sal y compiten por ser su favorito, pero las cosas se complican cuando tratan de usar las mágicas líneas de Nazca a su favor.

title: The End of Muscle Man
description: The guys want to help Muscle Man finish his bucket list.

title: Speed Demon
description: Batman has to enlist the help of Jason Blood, aka the Demon, when Brother Blood turns the Batmobile into a sentient, demonic entity.

title: The Law

When Gumball objects he is told that even the smallest misdemeanor can lead to a breakdown in law. In an effort to impress the kids Donut Cop takes them for a ride-along in his cop car and gets carried away, progressively breaking the law himself. He soon proves that the tiniest offense can indeed snowball into complete lawlessness!

title: First Flight

However Richard is terrified of flying, so Unikitty & Puppycorn spend the chaotic flight trying to help Rick conquer his fear of flying while Dr Fox joins Hawk in the cockpit to help him pass his test. After a destructive and dangerous flight, Rick makes it safetly back on the ground (after surviving the plane crashing). Hawk fails his test but gets to take it again next week, so the gang is excited for another free flight.

Will she resort to her own dirty tricks to win the election or stay true to her self and try to win by being nice?
